source.name: Individuals with Disabilities Education Act (IDEA) Data - Part B: Child Count (2009)
source.description: This State-level data about school-aged children with disabilities (ages 3-21), served under the Individuals with Disabilities Education Act (IDEA) - Part B, supports the collection, analysis and reporting of IDEA data about special education and related services, and the forms and spreadsheets used for collection.
